OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAI chatbots 'may soon be   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmore intelligent than us'  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man widely seen as the godfather of  
OL,6, artificial intelligence (AI) has quit  
OL,7, his job, warning about the growing     
OL,8, dangers from developments in the field.
OL,10,FGeoffrey Hinton, 75, announced his     
OL,11,Fresignation from Google in a statement 
OL,12,Fto the New York Times, saying he now   
OL,13,Fregretted his work.                    
OL,15,FHe told the BBC some of the dangers of 
OL,16,FAI chatbots were "quite scary".        
OL,18,F"Right now, they're not more           
OL,19,Fintelligent than us, as far as I can   
OL,20,Ftell. But I think they soon may be."   
